<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA10">
<l>maṇṇu malaiyu maṟikaṭalu mārutamum</l>
<l>viṇṇum viḻuṅkiyatu meyyeṉpa – reṇṇi</l>
<l>lalakaḷavu kaṇṭacī rāḻiyāyk kaṉṟiv</l>
<l>vulakaḷavu muṇṭōvuṉ vāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Earth, mountain, churning sea, wind and sky</l>
<l>were swallowed that day, they say truthfully, by you</l> 
<l>with the discus whose fame is seen as of incalculable measure.</l>
<l>Is it of this world’s measure, your mouth?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
